column5: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_McKinley> dbo:wikiPageRedirects ?x . ?x <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/locatedInArea> ?uri. ?uri rdf:type yago:WikicatStatesOfTheUnitedStates }
column6: In which U.S. state is Mount McKinley located?

column5: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Fort_Knox dbo:location ?uri . ?uri dbo:country res:United_States }
